---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import FeatureBlock from '../components/FeatureBlock.astro';
---
<Layout title="Insight Hunter Full Enterprise">
  <Hero />
  <section class="container">
    <p style="font-size:2.2rem; margin:60px 0 32px;">Insight Hunter Full Enterprise serves as the GAAP-aligned, AI-powered autonomous FP&A platform for finance-heavy organisations and scaling enterprises.</p>
    <p>This edition encompasses all Standard capabilities with advanced automations, role-based team access, comprehensive audit trails, and priority support. Integrate Scout for robust what-if scenarios, modeling impacts from headcount, market conditions, or revenue streams with high accuracy.</p>
    <p>New additions include an AI CFO mode for instant strategic recommendations, anomaly detection, and benchmarks tailored to industries (SaaS, agencies, retention). Optional part-time human CFO consulting provides expert guidance on complex scenarios. Generate board-ready reports, payout analyses, and custom operational metrics effortlessly.</p>
    <p>Full supports multi-currency consolidation, demand forecasting, and revenue leak detection, ensuring zero blind spots in financial operations.</p>
    <img src="/images/full-mockup.png" alt="Full Enterprise AI CFO dashboard" class="feature-image">
    <p>Designed for complete control and compliance at scale. Contact for custom implementation and pricing details.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="cta" style="display:inline-block; margin:60px auto;">Request Demo & Quote</a>
  </section>

  <section class="container">
    <FeatureBlock title="AI CFO Intelligence" text="Chat-based AI provides tailored advice, benchmarks, and predictive insights connected to your full data ecosystem." image="/images/ai-query-mockup.png" alt="AI CFO interface" />
    <FeatureBlock title="Human-Backed Expertise" text="Optional dedicated CFO support for strategic reviews and custom modeling." image="/images/teams-mockup.png" alt="Human CFO collaboration" reverse />
  </section>
</Layout>
